## L0 to L1 Upgrade

To upgrade this workspace from local-only (L0) to L1 compute (JupyterHub):

1. Read `{{adna_folder}}/how/skills/skill_l1_upgrade.md` — the phased upgrade guide
2. Run `{{adna_folder}}/prepare_for_onboarding.sh` — pre-flight checks and environment prep
3. Follow Phase 1 of the upgrade skill (requires admin to push `latlab` repo)
4. After upgrade: `latlab/` appears as a workspace peer. Update this file's `compute_tier` to `L1`.

For full self-service (no admin needed), a public L1 deployment package is planned but not yet available.

